[1]Rĩrĩa Jesũ oigĩre atĩrĩ,Nĩndarikia wĩra thĩ.Nĩoire maĩ na igũrũ,Agĩthambia Arutwo ake nyarĩri.Tũrorie maitho na igũrũ,Turĩ ndungata cia Roho,Ũmĩriru na ũtheru,Nicĩo hingũro cĩa igũrũ.[2]Utũkũ ũcĩo nĩahoire.Na agithithina thakame.Ya gũkũra mĩoyo iitũ.Ũkombo-inĩ wa shaitani.[3]Ariũ a thoguo na ariũ a nyũkwa.Na arĩa mwari thiritũ ĩmwe,Nĩo makoya kĩboko na karamu magũtuĩre.[4]Rĩrĩa mũthenya ũgakinya,Wa gũcoka kwa Mwathani.Nĩtũgakena mũno,Tũkirorera ũthiũ wake.[5]Hĩndĩ ĩyo ndũrĩrĩ ciothe,Nĩikarira na igirĩke.Tondũ mũndũ nĩakoragio,Nĩ Ngai wira ũrĩa atũire arutaga.[6]Tiga kũriganĩrwoKana kũgondagĩrĩraArahũka na ihenya,Nĩguo utoragie Shaitani
